Detailed Description

This class for vcard importation.

The following example demonstrates how to use the VCardImporter class.

 gaia::core::Context* mpContext = new gaia::core::Context(this);
 // We set the fourth parameter to be NULL for this sample,
 // and then it only parse the InputStream.
 // MyHandler class inherits class VCardEntryHandler to implement it.
 gaia::vcard::VCardEntryHandler* mpMyHandler = new MyHandler(this);
 gaia::vcard::VCardImporter importer
                 = gaia::vcard::VCardImporter(mpMyHandler);
 gaia::core::ContentResolver* cr = mpContext->getContentResolver();
 int32_t resId = R::raw::v40_sort_as;
 gaia::storage::InputStream* is =
                 mpContext->getResources()->openRawResource(resId);
 importer.import(*is);
